'''''Thought: A Journal of Philosophy''''' is a twice-annual [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] published by [[Wiley-Blackwell]] for the [[Northern Institute of Philosophy]]. The journal covers [[logic]], [[philosophy of maths]], [[philosophy of mind]], [[epistemology]], [[philosophy of language]], and [[metaphysics]]. The [[editor-in-chief|editors-in-chief]] are [[Crispin Wright]] ([[New York University]]), John Divers ([[University of Leeds]]), and [[Carrie Ichikawa Jenkins|Carrie Jenkins]] ([[University of British Columbia]]).
